{"tid":467479,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"長澤正美山田孝之演重拍《每天愛妳第一次》","createTime":"2017-11-13T14:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T14:37:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8c46fce525d51f8c23f982f07670e4d036ec7de8","tid":467479,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"30歲日本女星長澤正美和34歲男星山田孝之，自2007年合作電影《等待，是為了和妳相遇》後，相隔10年再結片緣，共同擔正改編自阿當桑迪拿（Adam Sandler）夥拍祖娜芭莉摩亞（Drew Barrymore）舊作的愛情喜劇《每天愛妳第一次》，並由《銀魂》導演福田雄一操刀，百分之一百在夏威夷取景。<br />\n山田孝之飾演在瓦胡島兼職導遊工作的花弗男大輔，偶遇長澤正美飾演、只有一天記憶的瑠依，他每天都施展不同的追求攻勢，希望得到女方的芳心，還預告兩人會咀戲連場。電影預定明年6月1日在日本開畫，電影公司今天搶先公開兩位主角頭貼頭的甜蜜蜜造型照。"},{"pid":"15d3a72ce056c07b2f57fd6a8649672e6d973038","tid":467479,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171107/photo/bkn-20171107181717028-1107_00862_001_01p.jpg?20171107211127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171107%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171107181717028-1107_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20171107211127&h=754df0d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91c3c538caec39c0cd0a05d643222fd34e2f19fc","tid":467479,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171107/photo/bkn-20171107181717028-1107_00862_001_03p.jpg?20171107211127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171107%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171107181717028-1107_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20171107211127&h=ac763cdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20171107/photo/bkn-20171107181717028-1107_00862_001_04p.jpg?20171107211127..\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20171107%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171107181717028-1107_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F2017110721